tio of EBITDA to consolidated debt service shall be required to be greater than or equal to 1.25 to 1.00 unless free liquidity is greater than $ 300,000,000 and (iii) increased certain of the baskets applicable to our ability to incur debt.

Also in December 2022, all of NCLC&#8217;s export-credit backed facilities were amended to conform the financial covenants with the Senior Secured Credit Facility. 

